&lt;li&gt;Maintain pricing discipline and margin ownership while closing commercially sound deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Technical Sales Engineering, Product, and internal stakeholders to advance opportunities and resolve technical questions&lt;/li&gt;
