&lt;p&gt;That said, &lt;strong&gt;we will make exceptions for truly exceptional talent if you live outside one of our hubs.&lt;/strong&gt; If you&#39;re the right person for this role, we&#39;ll have a conversation about what works.&lt;/p&gt;
