&lt;p&gt;Giga Energy is seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;BIM Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to oversee the development and integration of Building Information Models (BIM) across our data center construction portfolio. This role is responsible for coordinating all project stakeholders — architects, structural, MEP, and civil disciplines — to optimize the design, construction, and operation phases of mission-critical projects. The BIM Lead manages digital construction data, enforces model integrity, and drives the workflows that allow Giga&#39;s projects to be delivered with speed, accuracy, and constructability.&lt;/p&gt;
