&lt;p&gt;That said, &lt;strong&gt;we will make exceptions for truly exceptional talent if you live outside one of our hubs.&lt;/strong&gt; If you&#39;re the right person for this role, we&#39;ll have a conversation about what works.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Model Development &amp;amp; Coordination&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, manage, and update BIM models supporting design, construction, and operational handover.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with architects, structural engineers, MEP engineers, civil engineers, and other stakeholders to ensure model accuracy and consistency across disciplines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct clash detection and lead the resolution of coordination issues using Navisworks, Revit, or equivalent tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate regular coordination meetings to review model progress, identify issues, and develop resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure effective communication and collaboration across all internal teams and external partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Standards, Quality, and BIM Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, Implement and enforce BIM standards, protocols, naming conventions, and best practices across all projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, maintain, and manage &lt;strong&gt;BIM Execution Plans (BEP)&lt;/strong&gt; for each project.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform quality control checks and model audits to ensure compliance with Giga standards and project requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide feedback to project teams to drive continuous improvement in modeling practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain Revit templates, family libraries, and shared content to support consistent project delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
