&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where you&#39;ll work&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an on-site position that requires long term travel and/ or short term relocation. This person should be comfortable with 3-6 month periods of being at a location before moving to the next.&lt;/p&gt;
