&lt;li&gt;Ensure all work meets NEC, local codes, and project specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and correct deficiencies in workmanship before system energization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the on-site authority for electrical best practices and troubleshooting&lt;/li&gt;
